      <p>
        New documentary, <span style="font-style: italic;">All to Play For</span>, follows the journey of the 18 players that form the team FC Pol Positiu. Young Men are the most at-risk demographic on the mental health compass. They have limited spaces where they can be open about their conditions, without the fear of stigma. The changing rooms, bench and pitch of FC Pol Positiu, are one of those spaces.
